PRODUCT SPECIFICATION

**AgentOS**

*The universal AI agent for your PC*

Version 0.1 — March 2026

**CONFIDENTIAL**

# Table of contents

# 1. Executive summary

## 1.1. Vision

AgentOS is a desktop application that installs like a game, runs like an operating system, and thinks like a team of specialists. It is an AI-powered agent that can fully control a PC (screen, keyboard, mouse, CLI, file system), communicate through messaging platforms (Telegram, WhatsApp, Discord), and intelligently route tasks to the optimal AI model based on complexity, type, and cost.

The core innovation is threefold:

- An intelligent LLM Gateway that automatically selects the best AI brain for each task, optimizing for both quality and cost.

- A hierarchical agent system with Junior, Specialist, Senior, Manager, and Orchestrator levels that assembles the right team for any job.

- The Context Folder Protocol — an open specification that lets anyone create, share, and sell agent behaviors using simple files: markdown instructions and step-by-step screenshots.

## 1.2. Why now

2026 is the year of AI agents. Anthropic (Computer Use), OpenAI (Operator), Google (Project Mariner), and Microsoft (Copilot Actions) are all investing billions. But all share the same limitations: locked to their ecosystem, hard to customize, expensive to run, and impossible for non-engineers to teach new tasks. AgentOS fills this gap by being provider-agnostic, locally-installed, and radically simple to use.

